{"id":810667,"date":[{"year":1990,"month":3,"day":1}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"笔会","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"241","ytitle":"","mtitle":"倾诉生活","ftitle":"——读乃·让德富木刻《生活的倾诉》","authors":["刘原"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，猎猎作响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你肥大的裤管猎猎作响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疾走的风悄然无声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但在你嶙峋的双腿间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风舒展地摇响了尖细的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风铃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你伫立在鹅卵石路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一动不动，象一头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打扮过的猩猩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为宿命的灵感兀降"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以等待化成一具石雕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你瘦瘦的手撑着身后的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栏杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手臂里的血管仿佛粗过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里面的血却干涸了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再流动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不向任何人乞讨东西"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不知魂魄盘旋在哪里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦恼袭来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的忧愁其实微若小雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时下在阳光里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干得很快"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而青春的我在恍惚间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总感觉你晦涩的目光并"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未凝止"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我掠过你又走过大街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我确确实实感觉了猎猎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作响的风"}]}